parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Power Sliding Door Lock Actuator Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power sliding door lock actuator can cause the door to become stuck in a locked or unlocked position, making it difficult or impossible to open or close the door, which can lead to safety issues in emergency situations.
symptoms: The door makes a loud buzzing or squeaking noise
the door is stuck in a locked or unlocked position
the door cannot be opened or closed manually or remotely
the door actuator fails to function.
